== DATA
customer interactions
customer feedback
== METHODS
semi-supervised–training
That’s to use labeled data to train a powerful but impractically slow neural network, then use that network to label training data for a leaner, more efficient real-time network.
== RESULTS
personalized query responses
== ISSUES
violation of customer privacy
== SCORE
5
== COMMENTS
Recommendation systems and machine learning are widely used by online service providers to persuade customers to buy more than they need. These applications of ML should be more carfully monitored.